# SAHClock Project Rules

This project is a countdown clock for the Save American Hemp campaign.

## Project Details
- Target Date: November 12, 2026 at midnight
- Purpose: Advocacy countdown to raise awareness about federal hemp regulations
- Domain: SAVEHEMPCLOCK.COM
- GitHub: https://github.com/meezymeek/SAHClock

## Technology Stack
- Pure HTML/CSS/JavaScript (no build process needed)
- Flip library v1.8.2 (https://github.com/pqina/flip) for flip clock animations
- Hosted on GitHub Pages with custom domain

## Content Structure
1. H1: "Save American Hemp" (main title)
2. Flip countdown with Days on top row (full width), Hours/Minutes/Seconds on bottom row
3. H2: "Until Hemp is ILLEGAL" (subtitle)
4. Body text: Call to action about federal hemp rule
5. H3: "#SAVEAMERICANHEMP" (social media hashtag)
6. CTA Buttons: "Contact Your Legislators" and "Hemp News"
7. Subtle footer with creator attribution

## Design Guidelines
- Monochromatic gray color scheme throughout
- Classic flip clock style with dark gray panels (#3d3d3d)
- Fully responsive design for all screen sizes
- Clean, professional advocacy messaging

## Deployment
- Git repository initialized and pushed to GitHub
- CNAME file configured for custom domain
- Ready for GitHub Pages deployment
- DNS setup needed in Cloudflare
